{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2093704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以胡适是个很具有美国影子的民国文人特点，是民主主义的，但不是新民主主义的", "timestamp": 1626651839, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093708, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他早期提倡的自由那些至少在那个时候的中国是很新鲜的，要是胡适那么清高了他也就不可能是个典型的民国文人形象了", "timestamp": 1626651920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093729, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "胡适放八十年代估计就是方励之刘晓波一类人了", "timestamp": 1626652910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": 2093729, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 方励之有啥问题吗？", "timestamp": 1626654022, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093756, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": 2093752, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没什么问题啊，只是代表那个年代的思潮罢了", "timestamp": 1626654115, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": 2093752, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 刘晓波也没啥问题。", "timestamp": 1626654350, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": 2093765, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是。就算有问题也不至于关到死", "timestamp": 1626654746, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": 2093775, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 必须关上三百年doge", "timestamp": 1626656175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2093888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 407366, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "爱国的定义是什么，怕的是以